data.meta_description: os-h102_2012-01 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. DET Norske Veritas (DNV) is an autonomous and independent foundation with the objectives of safeguarding life, property and the environment, at sea and onshore. DNV undertakes classification, certification, and other verification and consultancy services relating to quality of ships, offshore units and installations, and onshore industries worldwide.
